---
import "../../styles/global.css";
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Contact — MCZ" description="Get in touch with the MCZ project maintainers.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-xl px-6 py-16 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg2">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-[32px] font-normal text-fg mb-8">Contact</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">MCZ is an open-source project. The best ways to reach us:</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">Bug reports & feature requests</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/nghyane/mcz/issues" class="text-accent underline hover:no-underline">GitHub Issues</a>. Please include your MCZ version, OS, and steps to reproduce.</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">General questions</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Start a <a href="https://github.com/nghyane/mcz/discussions" class="text-accent underline hover:no-underline">GitHub Discussion</a> for questions about the format, integration help, or feature ideas.</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-fg mt-8 mb-3">Email</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">For private inquiries: <a href="mailto:nghyane@gmail.com" class="text-accent underline hover:no-underline">nghyane@gmail.com</a></p>
  </article>
</Base>
